      <title>南非工会坚决要求拉马福萨继续担任总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/south-africa-elections-unions-want-ramaphosa-to-remain-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非最强大的工会联合会与非洲人国民大会结盟，该联合会表示，该党在上周灾难性的选举表现后达成的任何联盟协议都必须确保总统西里尔·拉马福萨保住他的职位，并遵守其宣言中的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/south-africa-elections-unions-want-ramaphosa-to-remain-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 11:15:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
